WEBVTT

00:00.120 --> 00:04.240
You guys know I love my dresses and my fancy outfits,

00:04.240 --> 00:07.020
but I don't wear that 24 7.

00:07.120 --> 00:08.080
And when I don't,

00:08.080 --> 00:09.840
I need a really good sweatpant.

00:09.840 --> 00:12.740
And something that I need is something comfortable,

00:12.800 --> 00:13.400
long enough,

00:13.400 --> 00:17.700
because I'm 6 foot tall and just easy to move in.

00:19.720 --> 00:23.340
I love these Aritzia sweat fleece sweatpants.

00:23.560 --> 00:26.160
They come in so many different colors,

00:26.160 --> 00:28.160
and these are my two favorite ones.

00:28.160 --> 00:30.280
I love a neutral color, but then

00:30.280 --> 00:33.080
I'm also trying to branch out into wearing color.

00:33.080 --> 00:34.640
I don't know how I feel about it yet,

00:34.640 --> 00:36.320
but we're working on it.

00:36.320 --> 00:38.580
They're so comfy on the inside,

00:38.760 --> 00:40.920
and they come in two different lengths,

00:40.920 --> 00:43.440
so I usually always go with the tall.

00:43.440 --> 00:44.640
These sweats

00:44.640 --> 00:46.880
are what I wear when I've clocked in for the night

00:46.880 --> 00:48.080
and I'm just done with my day

00:48.080 --> 00:49.217
and ready to get comfortable.
